{"tid":216721,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"左手只需輕輕扶着....","createTime":"2017-04-25T11:38:33.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-26T03:09:58.000Z","uid":1208,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"04186112bb07c28cb55b01417287c2efe35158db","tid":216721,"uid":1208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T11:38:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n睇返最後果幾話啲分鏡，每次睇都好緊張<br />\n十幾年前既漫畫已經咁神<br />\n<br />\n尤其尾二進攻同最後果球<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3iO59Oc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3iO59Oc.jpg&h=db0c08a2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/25/193647_3d076f04b461038402115e124894403d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F25%2F193647_3d076f04b461038402115e124894403d.jpg&h=3729e017&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/25/193648_4b3bfc6b65e00d7bc6ffae3a63919b88.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F25%2F193648_4b3bfc6b65e00d7bc6ffae3a63919b88.jpg&h=2170c5cb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/30r86EK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F30r86EK.jpg&h=5ab7e726&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n到呢幕<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/25/192934_afb0a446817617e3ebdbc94a3fd95028.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F25%2F192934_afb0a446817617e3ebdbc94a3fd95028.jpg&h=8eb409b7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n而家感覺都無哂呢個程度既漫畫<br />\n有無人最近有睇返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee3befd9ce187ed594f6b1bb4a96ed2a93458893","tid":216721,"uid":46140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T13:43:25.000Z","msg":"一睇就起雞皮"},{"pid":"53aefb0cb340858fdc1d3f38e9f33ebfeb46b478","tid":216721,"uid":4402,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T13:49:05.000Z","msg":"老頭子，你最光輝的時代是全日本時代嗎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36ea686769f96d9f9c988eb8a4c80bf1c9c00c66","tid":216721,"uid":1208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T14:02:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>老頭子，你最光輝的時代是全日本時代嗎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢個我都有cap <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0en9338.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0en9338.jpg&h=bda0de4a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/25/220220_2e9b230e5ef3203707cda8ab4c1a5bea.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F25%2F220220_2e9b230e5ef3203707cda8ab4c1a5bea.jpg&h=43d1013d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n喊撚左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e69c02a728a6f2488d944791d54d220d87217f3","tid":216721,"uid":45536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T01:18:57.000Z","msg":"真係好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"518a337cf9db2c40602d19f3792582852901b31c","tid":216721,"uid":8500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T01:20:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c05b3eb534aff07779381ad9043665693ec79d1","tid":216721,"uid":62935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T01:22:17.000Z","msg":"要聽埋首歌"},{"pid":"3cc5044db83356104798bae1b56a4b1842e51056","tid":216721,"uid":31306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy"