ockquote>如果唔腰斬一落講到櫻木三年級做隊長就好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n無左赤木同三井<br />\n打西咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"883c534ef4526abf4428629fd834b80e55d34540","tid":216721,"uid":59669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T01:37:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>如果唔腰斬一落講到櫻木三年級做隊長就好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote></blockquote><br />\n而家完得好好<br />\n拖長盞爛<br />\n山王加沢北已經係最强<br />\n打贏咗之後仲想點寫<br />\n又好似啲王道漫咁有更強嘅對手？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8dcbfeb999bca440ab942f700228839f5992322e","tid":216721,"uid":1424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T01:37:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果唔腰斬一落講到櫻木三年級做隊長就好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我反而覺得咁樣變皇道漫無而家咁好<br />\n留番d 遺憾"},{"pid":"2fb55ecb01edcb053523322763845b58019f2d90","tid":216721,"uid":10214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T01:38:29.000Z","msg":"晴子小姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2907cd3c2a298820e7d0ab48d55e261170152456","tid":216721,"uid":23919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T01:44:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>如果唔腰斬一落講到櫻木三年級做隊長就好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔係咁樣完左嘅,你點會到而家都仲覺得神<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45833ad6bb9befb3e044cef68da3d3dcab0c0bb1","tid":216721,"uid":36839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T02:14:56.000Z","msg":"Slam dunk 真係好神<br />\n每次睇都起晒雞皮<br />\n我覺得咁完係最好，打敗左最強嘅山王<br />\n如果寫落去，反而成個故事無咁靚"},{"pid":"09c4667ce16d00aac5028433db5d5bffc4e05868","tid":216721,"uid":49912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T02:48:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>如果唔腰斬一落講到櫻木三年級做隊長就好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote></blockquote><br />\n而家完得好好<br />\n拖長盞爛<br />\n山王加沢北已經係最强<br />\n<br />\n打贏咗之後仲想點寫<br />\n又好似啲王道漫咁有更強嘅對手？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n仲有諸星大同埋O'neal舖左未講<br />\n<br />\n同埋可以講櫻木傷住打所以狀態不佳<br />\n流川楓暫借過美國離隊等等"},{"pid":"79786bf184d475abd0c07357ab9627e45914a28b","tid":216721,"uid":19958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T02:52:15.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/QyKAl5B4aPY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FQyKAl5B4aPY&d=fUB9jTkReJc3fMEQQRliu8PrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=17362f17\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/QyKAl5B4aPY</a><br />\n<br />\n呢段片睇幾多次都喊左出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e43f70358b4dcaa5f341df0ea9e39fdb07a637b","tid":216721,"uid":59669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T03:09:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>如果唔腰斬一落講到櫻木三年級做隊長就好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote></blockquote><br />\n而家完得好好<br />\n拖長盞爛<br />\n山王加沢北已經係最强<br />\n<br />\n打贏咗之後仲想點寫<br />\n又好似啲王道漫咁有更強嘅對手？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n仲有諸星大同埋O'neal舖左未講<br />\n<br />\n同埋可以講櫻木傷住打所以狀態不佳<br />\n流川楓暫借過美國離隊等等</blockquote><br />\n諸星冇嘢好講<br />\n佢自己都話冇信心贏到沢北<br />\n流川走，猩猩去大學<br />\n唔係呢五個人仲有咩好睇<br />\n格硬寫姐係要寫新角加"},{"pid":"35199883072bf7f5a0c2dac04401b6bb9b7ac9d9","tid":216721,"uid":59669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T03:09:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>如果唔腰斬一落講到櫻木三年級做隊長就好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote></blockquote><br />\n而家完得好好<br />\n拖長盞爛<br />\n山王加沢北已經係最强<br />\n<br />\n打贏咗之後仲想點寫<br />\n又好似啲王道漫咁有更強嘅對手？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n仲有諸星大同埋O'neal舖左未講<br />\n<br />\n同埋可以講櫻木傷住打所以狀態不佳<br />\n流川楓暫借過美國離隊等等</blockquote><br />\n諸星冇嘢好講<br />\n佢自己都話冇信心贏到沢北<br />\n流川走，猩猩去大學<br />\n唔係呢五個人仲有咩好睇<br />\n格硬寫姐係要寫新角加</blockquote><br />\n加入又由LV1開始咁"}]}